House Rules FIGHTER CLASS HIGH LEVEL ABILITIES:

-  Level 15: POWER ATTACK
A Power Attack allows the warrior to strike blows so forceful that they stun an opponent for 2 rounds if it fails its save vs. death at a -4 penalty. The ability lasts for 2 rounds.

-  Level 20: WHIRLWIND ATTACK
This ability allows the warrior to unleash a flurry of super-fast blows.  The ability sets one's number of attacks per round to 10 without penalties, the whirlwind attack lasts for one round.

-  Level 25: CRITICAL STRIKE
A high-level warrior's intimate knowledge of vital spots on opponents allows him to, once per day, concentrate all of the attacks in one round to strike a vital area every time. With this ability, every attack roll made in the next round is a natural 20, a critical hit.

-  Level 30: CRITICAL STRIKE
The warrior gains an additional use of Critical Strike.
~
