House Rules PALADIN CLASS HIGH LEVEL ABILITIES:

-  Level 15: RESIST MAGIC
This ability allows the paladin to temporarily tap a great inner strength and fight off the effects of malevolent magic. For 4 rounds the paladin's magic resistance is set to 50%. This is not cumulative with other forms of magic resistance so if the paladin already has 50% magic resistance or greater, the ability is useless.

-  Level 20: WHIRLWIND ATTACK
